(1, 'Where can I get some?', 'French', 1, 1, '253 Street', 'Fr', '6789', '2014-07-10 17:28:00', '2014-07-17 17:55:00', '646-2352-q.jpg', '<p>\r\n	There are many variations of passages of Lorem Ipsum available</p>\r\n', 'codinghero.net', 'codinghero.net', '', 1, '2014-07-10 17:29:00', '2014-07-17 09:08:21'),
(3, 'Where does it come from?', 'Germany', 1, 1, '63594-Hasselroth', 'Darmstadt', '63594', '2014-07-08 00:00:00', '2014-07-31 00:00:00', '7055-3888-a.jpg', '<p>\r\n	Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text</p>\r\n', 'Li Europan lingues es membres ', 'Li Europan lingues es membres ', '7795-past_perfect_or_past_perfect_continuous.pdf', 1, '2014-07-11 14:33:00', '2014-07-17 09:08:09'),
(4, 'Why do we use it?', 'Germany', 1, 1, '63594-Hasselroth', 'Darmstadt', '63594', '2014-07-24 00:00:00', '2014-07-31 00:00:00', '3578-3046-r.jpg', '<p>\r\n	It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content.</p>\r\n', 'Li Europan lingues es membres ', 'Li Europan lingues es membres ', '', 1, '2014-07-17 09:09:42', '2014-07-17 09:09:42'),
(5, 'Where can I get some?', 'Germany', 1, 1, '63594-Hasselroth', 'Darmstadt', '63594', '2014-07-24 00:00:00', '2014-07-31 00:00:00', '3760-9303-g.jpg', '<p>\r\n	Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry&#39;s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry&#39;s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book.</p>\r\n', '', '', '', 1, '2014-07-17 09:11:00', '2014-07-17 15:50:26'),
(6, 'What is Lorem Ipsum?', 'Germany', 1, 1, '63594-Hasselroth', 'Darmstadt', '63594', '2014-07-24 00:00:00', '2014-07-31 00:00:00', '886-3046-r.jpg', '<p>\r\n	<strong>Lorem Ipsum</strong> is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry&#39;s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book.Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry&#39;s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry&#39;s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book.</p>\r\n', 'Li Europan lingues es membres', 'Li Europan lingues es membres', '', 1, '2014-07-17 09:11:00', '2014-07-17 15:51:07');
